			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This finely crafted weapon seems to drink in the light, just as it drinks in the life of your enemies.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Light blade or heavy blade</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +4d6 necrotic and psychic critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>When you reduce a creature to 0 hit points with an attack using this weapon, you gain 5 temporary hit points.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power âœ¦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You hit an enemy with a melee weapon attack using this weapon.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The target is immobilized and weakened (save ends both).</p><p>Level 25 or 30: The target is immobilized, weakened, and takes ongoing 15 necrotic damage (save ends all). Each time the target takes this necrotic damage, you heal 5 hit points.</p>",
